one_reviews_text: I think I just spent 8 dollars to get married to a guy for 2 minutes. However, don't get me wrong getting married to this guy was one of (But not the) best experiences of my life up to this very moment. Hot, Deep Voiced, Assertive Somehow taller than me when I am 6' 3" gaming athlete. The works, but 2 minutes of paradise still doesn't seem like enough paradise for 8 dollars. Until communism kicks in with enough trial and error I can't see this being a good idea for your bottom dollar unless your FOMO is as bad as mine and you experience it for yourself like me anyway. TLDR: FOMO = FO:YES    87/15 - IGN
